title: The 2026 'Super Bowl of Astronomy' starts today — here's what's happening
description: Astronomers are gathering in Phoenix this week for the 247th meeting of the American Astronomical Society (AAS 247), where the latest discoveries from exoplanets, JWST and upcoming space missions will take center stage.
